  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Katagiri-san is relying on me\"  is an RPG game produced by プラスカゼット and published by Hanabi games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is the sequel to \"Katagiri-san is very cold\".</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331040/extras/cb5aa3f96eb6f40e4143ec83140cf517.avif?t=1743233970\" width=550 height=70 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up in a dimly lit room, with your classmate Katagiri-san in front of you. Why are you here? Who could've done it? Why is she here...? Wait a minute... I think you've been here once before. Everything looks the same, yet something seems off... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to find out what brought you back to this place in this short escape room RPG with hints of horror, comedy, and a bunch of sweets lying around! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331040/extras/16c2dc665637c3656ef7a771d2e7282c.avif?t=1743233970\" width=550 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331040/extras/eaffd37f61fe41c49a246725d7d9eee2.avif?t=1743233970\" width=550 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331040/extras/d2ed543f36b48584fbed5656e58cc05b.avif?t=1743233970\" width=550 height=70 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JRPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzle and Escape Mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Captivating Storyline</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Katagiri-san is relying on me\"  is an RPG game produced by プラスカゼット and published by Hanabi games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is the sequel to \"Katagiri-san is very cold\".</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331040/extras/cb5aa3f96eb6f40e4143ec83140cf517.avif?t=1743233970\" width=550 height=70 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up in a dimly lit room, with your classmate Katagiri-san in front of you. Why are you here? Who could've done it? Why is she here...? Wait a minute... I think you've been here once before. Everything looks the same, yet something seems off... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to find out what brought you back to this place in this short escape room RPG with hints of horror, comedy, and a bunch of sweets lying around! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331040/extras/16c2dc665637c3656ef7a771d2e7282c.avif?t=1743233970\" width=550 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331040/extras/eaffd37f61fe41c49a246725d7d9eee2.avif?t=1743233970\" width=550 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331040/extras/d2ed543f36b48584fbed5656e58cc05b.avif?t=1743233970\" width=550 height=70 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JRPG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzle and Escape Mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Captivating Storyline</p></li></ul>",
